        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="hero-section text-center mt-5">
    <h2 class="display-5">Efficient Dairy Management</h2>
    <p class="lead">Streamline your dairy operations with our state-of-the-art management system. Track milk production, manage orders, and ensure quality control with ease.</p>
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get Started</a>
</div>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/100/000000/milk-bottle.png" alt="Milk Production">
            <h3>Track Milk Production</h3>
            <p>Monitor and record milk production data accurately to enhance productivity and quality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/100/000000/purchase-order.png" alt="Manage Orders">
            <h3>Manage Orders</h3>
            <p>Efficiently handle customer orders and ensure timely delivery of dairy products.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/100/000000/checked.png" alt="Quality Control">
            <h3>Ensure Quality Control</h3>
            <p>Implement rigorous quality control measures to maintain high standards of dairy products.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="services-section bg-light mt-5 py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Our Services</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <i class="fas fa-cog fa-4x mb-3"></i>
                <h3>Customizable Solutions</h3>
                <p>Tailor our dairy management system to fit your specific needs and workflows.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line fa-4x mb-3"></i>
                <h3>Analytics and Reporting</h3>
                <p>Gain insights into your dairy operations with advanced analytics and reporting features.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <i class="fas fa-users fa-4x mb-3"></i>
                <h3>Customer Support</h3>
                <p>24/7 customer support to assist you in optimizing your dairy management processes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="contact-section mt-5 py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <p class="lead">Have questions or need assistance? Contact our team for support.</p>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email: info@dairymilkmanagement.com</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Phone: +92 (332866199)</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Address: 123 Dairy Farm Rd, Dairyville, Pakistan</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <p class="lead">You can also reach out to us using the form below:</p>
                <form>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Email">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <textarea class="form-control" rows="5" placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer class="border-top footer text-muted">
    <div class="container">
        &copy; 2024 - Dairy Milk Management - <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Privacy">Privacy</a>
    </div>
</footer>
